{"tid":1626190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（代人開po) 將軍澳中心有個仆街藍絲經理","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:21:40.000Z","uid":305730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"811c8027551c261fabbfaa0fc4671bf2cc6d269a","tid":1626190,"uid":305730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"代店員姐姐開po<br />\n尋日大概下晝四五點<br />\n有個靚女店員喺將軍澳中心吉龍糖播緊國歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n播播下有個仆街藍絲商場經理過黎問係咪有人搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就話有人投訴受到滋擾<br />\n之後店員姐姐話會校細聲啲<br />\n但係過左無耐店長就打電話黎話唔好繼續播<br />\n咁店員姐姐就唯有停左首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後個仆街藍絲商場經理就喺隔離笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來就喺個仆街商場經理打電話比吉龍糖店長<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家認住呢條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vhh7muz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvhh7muz.jpg&h=9f518573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmFs5Y2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmFs5Y2.jpg&h=21913ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6Adg6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6Adg6M.jpg&h=6e609e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過記住支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n店員姐姐仲比左員工七折優惠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"193bf5ae66c53c5ef938eaf678e13a2864c40204","tid":1626190,"uid":210260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"鶳咗未<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人反抗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"877a8e9ce19ad997972a2f482c2dda33c9ebd204","tid":1626190,"uid":227982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"呢個肥佬係好撚串，明明食q黎咋"}]}